Pvl_checkif
===========

Description:

Check if a value is in a list (default separator: |)

You can use global vars in parameters, they will be parsed!

------------------------------------------------------

Examples:
{exp:pvl_checkif value="123" is_in="1|12|123" [separator="|"]}
	<p>Yes Sire!</p>
{/exp:pvl_checkif}

{exp:pvl_checkif value="{member_id}" is_in="1|5"}
	<p>You've got the power!</p>
{/exp:pvl_checkif}

------------------------------------------------------